column12:
'desc': [u'

MeeMee Baby Cradle (Multicolor) Price: Rs.7495

Key Features

  • Wheels can be Pinned Down to One Place
  • Curb the Cradle form Rolling Down on its Own
  • Lock the Cradle from Rocking Using the Locking Pin
  • Gentle Rocking Motion

A cradle is one most soothing and comforting accessory that can gently rock your little angel to sleep. Mee Mee’s Wooden Cradle is safe cradle that has a water-proof pad. This Cradle from Mee Mee has a gentle rocking motion and you can lock the cradle from rocking using the locking pin. The caster wheels on the cradle make the cradle easily portable; you can effortlessly take the cradle wherever you want to. The wheels can be pinned down to one place and curb the cradle form rolling down on its own.

The mosquito net on the cradle will keep your darling safe and protected. There is a pouch on the Mee Mee Cradle that can be used to store your baby’s accessories and toys. Mee Mee Wooden Cradle has original wood with no paint that makes it all the more safe to be used for children. This Mee Mee Cradle has dimensions of 99 x 61 x 85 cm and weighs between 12 and 13 kg.

']
